duction of CXL and PCIe 5.0. In addition, we propose\npossible countermeasures that software developers, hardware designers, and\nsystem administrators can use to suppress the observed side-channel leakages\nand analyze their implicit costs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Feb 2022 16:59:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Mar 2023 16:51:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-10"}
