 mechanism of strong magneto-electric effects via\nstrain interactions in CoFe2O4/PMN-PT composite.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 09:48:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-25"}
