 process by seamlessly integrating\nmultiple routine procedures. The one-stop solution shortens the time scale it\ntakes to ready the first treatment from days to minutes, significantly\nimproving the patient experience and the efficiency of the workflow, and shows\npotential to facilitate the clinical application of online adaptive replanning.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Feb 2022 10:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-25"}
